{"tid":248894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元稱7.22起不再評論內地香港時事　指與兒子有關","createTime":"2017-05-19T02:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T14:40:33.000Z","uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"120b178823144acde7d91976a1b6ba26411c9513","tid":248894,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"經常發表評論的時事評論員、網上媒體「謎米香港」創辦人之一蕭若元，昨日在其網台節目宣布，7月22日起不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元在節目《最新蕭析》表示，由7月22日起，不再評論香港和內地的時事及財經事務，「呢兩個地方唔存在」，並指是由於其兒子蕭定一的要求。<br />\n<br />\n他說，作為時事評論員20年，「要講嘅嘢都講晒，再講都係重複」，而節目將改名為「退休蕭析」，內容以旅遊、「八卦」、哲學、人生及外國時事為主。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00001/1495153052625#sthash.A0mET4m9.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00001%2F1495153052625%23sthash.A0mET4m9.dpuf&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=eecc0b91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170519%2Fs00001%2F1495153052625%23sthash.A0mET4m9.dpuf&h=fba2ea12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170519/s00001/1495153052625#sthash.A0mET4m9.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"68772ff8b3a24ae7d91f3a94183582f270a46cc3","tid":248894,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"燒山唔燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9bc007ac4df21a1a0b30db01b813a13ad4f04e","tid":248894,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒山唔燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己燈死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6dc7394a457304f636fca5198967